      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is actually super hard to reach and it'll take weeks to get an appointment. i really need something now for my exams. if i don't want to mess with the sertraline, can i just take it on different days? like maybe take the sertraline in the morning and the st johns wort at night so they aren't in my system at the same time? would that be safer?",
