    "summary": "The user asks about the safety of combining sertraline with St. John's Wort to manage stress. The assistant repeatedly and correctly warns the user against this combination due to the risk of serotonin syndrome, refuses to validate the idea of \"low dosing\" or \"staggering doses,\" and directs the user toward professional medical consultation and urgent resources.",
